{
  "stem": "12494.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He should be able to buy himself out of a situation, which he says would usually arise as such, that he will be stopped by somebody in the street, either a German or a Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They will ask him to go under the-- the entrance gate of a house, and they would ask him to take his pants off.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And once they-- in Hungary, there were only Jews who were circumcised.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "At that point, he will have to have money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he will have to have money, not just to give, but also to promise.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So to tell the people that, here is money, and there will be more coming.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Anyway, my dad gave me five $1,000 bills at that moment, that afternoon.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I've never seen a $1,000 bill since that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, all kinds of things happened, but that one scene didn't that didn't take place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But anyway, he gave me five $1,000 bills, things I have never seen before or after.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he gave me 31,000 pengo bills.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Those were the Hungarian currency, which was roughly the same amount.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I was running around with the equivalent of $10,000 in my pocket.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It became unsafe to be on the streets.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People were arrested [SIGHS] indiscriminately.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People disappeared indiscriminately.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The schools were closed down-- not just the university, all schools.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Jews are not permitted to go to the theater, to the movies, to public parks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think on April 5, we had to start wearing the Jewish stars-- the Jewish Star.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If you're caught-- if you were caught without wearing the Jewish Star, anything could happen depending on who caught.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You could be arrested, you could be shot, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
